title: place.availableTo
description:
The last date & time that the [place](../place.json) is allowed to be visible on publication channels.

Added automatically by UiTdatabank based on either the [startDate](./startDate) or [endDate](./endDate.json) depending on the [place type](./terms.json).

Formatted as an ISO-8601 datetime. For example `2021-05-17T22:00:00+00:00`.
